field1:{"type":"field","size":[180,189],"pos":[292,117],"locked":1,"border":0,"value":"By transitioning between several cards in sequence, potentially alternating go[] with sleep[] to introduce additional pauses, it is possible to string together elaborate \"slide show\" animations with only a single very simple script.\n\nDon't underestimate the creative potential of this technique!"}
